<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_cfb0a8f1-ae42-467a-9ddd-b2d7e5316072" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>D3D16</sptc><title id="_1a58f3ed-c275-4dcf-9e7f-c456de0a6a1a">Thresholds</title><archive-num/><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/2117_1.4.0.xml" variation="NSW" variation-type="REPLACE">NSW REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_ba348030-296b-457b-8fb4-a79aaae1348c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_070905c9-b495-4cbe-9817-4f4ba258843f">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The threshold of a doorway must not incorporate a step or ramp at any point closer to the doorway than the width of the door leaf unless the doorway opens to an external space; and—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_a9c9587b-d632-4117-b791-8a6a5cbb4f57">where the doorway serves an area <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_44473567-4db3-45a4-808d-0521be95634e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_fa1db741-0151-41ff-bbb8-533213da34bd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/26_0.10.0.xml#_0422da33-ebd2-4d7c-994c-31d8dad5aa0f" id="_02523fac-e6c8-4d27-ab69-c5b10b03f022" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-part">Part D4</xref>, it is provided with a threshold ramp or step ramp in accordance with AS 1428.1; or</li><li id="_af7918d9-2222-4c34-8a50-37b0ecb2bc08">where (a) does not apply, the door sill is not located below, and is not more than 190 mm above, the finished surface of the ground, balcony, or the like to which the doorway opens.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_60f3ebe7-27fe-495e-80d4-e12b6a8f81dd"><callout-type ncc-info-type="exemption"/><p>D3D16 does not apply to a plant room, machinery room, or the like.</p></callout><callout id="_fcffcac8-c1f0-472f-a1a4-2da19d30cbdc"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><title id="_95c965a0-d586-4021-b28a-efe17662fa9c">Read in conjunction with D4D3</title><p>D3D16(a) is to be read in conjunction with D4D3, which requires some external doorways to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_993031ad-6dfc-4262-8b12-52b7f6ca9259" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref>. In order to comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/2035_1.3.0.xml#_95b0e5ea-8488-4ba8-a40c-e60fa1eeed8e" id="_15d4b154-f72c-40b7-ad68-21193839310a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D4D3</xref>, the thresholds of these doorways cannot incorporate a ramp within the width of the door leaf.</p></callout><callout id="_1efded2c-8b8f-41f4-bbae-b31e2ed2221b"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><title id="_5d6f4772-ba01-46c8-8f06-57c0fd5769cd">Bunds</title><p>D3D16 does not prevent the addition of a bund within the width of the door leaf from the doorway. However, this is to be considered in conjunction with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/2034_1.14.0.xml#_396cb0f6-6ff5-49da-9c51-d4ba94a22e79" id="_e53b2f2c-5dc1-48f6-8a73-d6b1b219ee6d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D4D2</xref> that requires certain areas to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_12a184b6-31ad-4697-b921-9578848ef2d2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> which may prevent the incorporation of a bund.</p></callout></clause>